  <entry>
    <title>一个博客的诞生</title>
    <link href="/2021/02/22/%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%9E%E7%94%9F/"/>
    <url>/2021/02/22/%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%9E%E7%94%9F/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="环境配置"><a href="#环境配置" class="headerlink" title="环境配置"></a>环境配置</h2><h3 id="安装node"><a href="#安装node" class="headerlink" title="安装node"></a>安装node</h3><p><code>brew install node</code></p><p><img src="/%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%9E%E7%94%9F/huanj_1.png" alt="huanj_1"></p><h3 id="安装git"><a href="#安装git" class="headerlink" title="安装git"></a>安装git</h3><p><code>brew install git</code></p><h3 id="安装npm"><a href="#安装npm" class="headerlink" title="安装npm"></a>安装npm</h3><p><code>brew install npm</code></p><h3 id="Review"><a href="#Review" class="headerlink" title="Review"></a>Review</h3><p><code>node -v</code><br><code>git --version</code><br><code>npm -v</code></p><h3 id="安装hexo"><a href="#安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo"></a>安装hexo</h3><p><code>sudo npm install -g hexo-cli</code></p><h2 id="用Hexo搭建博客"><a href="#用Hexo搭建博客" class="headerlink" title="用Hexo搭建博客"></a>用Hexo搭建博客</h2><p>在桌面创建一个空文件夹blog</p><p>在blog路径下初始化一个博客</p><p><code>cd Desktop/blog</code><br><code>hexo init</code></p><p>启动hexo<br><code>hexo s</code></p><p>根据提示在浏览器中输入<a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000</a></p><p>至此，博客网页可以在本地运行与查看</p><p>命令行下ctrl+c，退出命令，仍然在blog目录下</p><h2 id="部署至Github"><a href="#部署至Github" class="headerlink" title="部署至Github"></a>部署至Github</h2><p>登录Github，新建一个仓库New repository，仓库名称必须为：昵称.github.io</p><p>在blog路径下安装git部署插件：<code>npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></p><p>更改blog文件夹下，_config.yml的配置</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">deploy:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">git</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">repo:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://github.com/ManjiaLiang/ManjiaLiang.github.io.git</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">branch:</span> <span class="hljs-string">master</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>回到命令行部署到远端</p><p><code>hexo d</code></p><h2 id="搞个主题"><a href="#搞个主题" class="headerlink" title="搞个主题"></a>搞个主题</h2>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
